\pard\f0\fs28   Sect. HORMINUM Dumort. Annuals. Calyx tubular, deflexed in fruit. Upper lip of corolla more or less straight; tube without a ring of hairs inside. Staminal connective longer than filament; arms unequal, the shorter more or less dolabriform.
\par

